latestPosts.caption:
Designed as part of Jigar & Nikita’s Rang Mahal collection, Seema’s wedding lehenga is a tribute to her strength and grace. The regal peacock, woven into every detail, reflects her spirit, making this creation even more special.

Watch Jigar & Nikita share their honour in bringing Nykaa Wali Bride Seema’s dream to life in Nykaa Wali Shaadi, Episode 3 - now streaming on JioCinema! 

#Nykaa #NykaaWaliShaadi

Designing for a bride who serves the nation- an honor beyond words! 🇮🇳✨ 

Jigar & Nikita bring their artistry to Seema, an army officer whose courage is as inspiring as her love story. Watch it all unfold in Nykaa Wali Shaadi, now streaming on JioCinema!

Produced by @zoieakhtar @reemakagti1 
Directed by @ashwinkumar23 @totalsiddharth 
Outfit by @jigarandnikitaofficial @jigarshah0905 @nikitamurarka24

✨Big News! ✨
We are thrilled to be part of a cinematic journey starring Shantanu Maheshwari and Avneet Kaur for a groundbreaking film supported by the Vietnam government! 🎥✨

This cinematic masterpiece beautifully weaves a tale of emotions, culture, and artistry. 🌏 Stay tuned as it takes center stage on a global platform.

We absolutely love styling them for their incredible journey, bringing our designs to life on such a remarkable stage.

Shop the latest collection In-store: Visit us at our flagship store- Santacruz West, Mumbai
Online store: www.jigarnikita.com
